window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>They came in peace. But that was last time…</b></p> <p>As the world gears up for the first anniversary of Contact Day, Dan McCarthy’s year-long effort to stay out of the limelight collapses in an instant.</p> <p>A direct call from the Messengers throws Dan into urgent action, but the fallout plants a troubling seed of doubt:</p> <p>This time, maybe they didn’t come here to <i>help</i>....</p>"; 
